Usage: createUserDisableForCombLoopBreak [-help] -input_file <string>
                                         -outfile <string>

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-input_file <string>     # Specify the disabled time arcs report generated by
                         # third-party tool. (string, required)
-outfile <string>        # Specify the name of the output SDC file.
                         # (string, required)